{"id":232954389,"title":"心中真正萬年不敗的古早味零食","content":"現在人飲食充裕，選擇多樣\n所以會在吃這一塊講究都是很正常的\n不過現在有很多東西好吃是好吃\n但還是無法替代一些已經賣了數十年的古早味點心\n古早味點心大家想到的不外乎王子麵，足球巧克力，麵茶粉，香菸糖，可樂瓶造型軟糖，海底雞，滋露巧克力，可以抽數量的綠豆糕跟蜜地瓜條........等等\n這些零食固然經典\n但常常過於甜膩\n在小弟心目中真正有歷史又好吃的零食就是它\n👇👇👇👇👇\nhttps://i.imgur.com/nWCIVKZ.jpg\n\n孔雀餅乾，賣了五十年口味始終如一\n蛋香跟餅乾的酥香味讓人一口接一口，差點停不下來\n唯一的缺點就是有點乾，吃的時候配些飲品比較好\n各位卡友們是否也有自己喜歡的古早味零食呢😁😁","excerpt":"現在人飲食充裕，選擇多樣，所以會在吃這一塊講究都是很正常的，不過現在有很多東西好吃是好吃，但還是無法替代一些已經賣了數十年的古早味點心，古早味點心大家想到的不外乎王子麵，足球巧克力，麵茶粉，香菸糖，可","anonymousSchool":false,"anonymousDepartment":true,"pinned":false,"forumId":"de977130-f3eb-467b-822e-b0e91124e9eb","replyId":null,"createdAt":"2020-01-25T06:34:40.212Z","updatedAt":"2020-01-25T06:34:40.212Z","commentCount":55,"likeCount":576,"tags":[],"topics":["零食","餅乾"],"supportedReactions":null,"withNickname":false,"reportReason":"","hiddenByAuthor":false,"meta":{"layout":"classic"},"forumName":"美食","forumAlias":"food","school":"遠東科技大學","replyTitle":null,"gender":"M","personaSubscriptable":null,"reactions":[{"id":"286f599c-f86a-4932-82f0-f5a06f1eca03","count":569},{"id":"e8e6bc5d-41b0-4129-b134-97507523d7ff","count":7}],"hidden":false,"customStyle":null,"isSuspiciousAccount":false,"layout":"classic","withImages":true,"withVideos":false,"media":[{"url":"https://i.imgur.com/nWCIVKZ.jpg"}],"reportReasonText":"","mediaMeta":[{"id":"893a20ec-7b70-4f17-a923-c43bfeaba0a5","url":"https://i.imgur.com/nWCIVKZl.jpg","normalizedUrl":"https://i.imgur.com/nWCIVKZl.jpg","thumbnail":"https://i.imgur.com/nWCIVKZl.jpg","type":"image/thumbnail","tags":["ANNOTATED"],"createdAt":"2020-01-25T06:34:40.212Z","updatedAt":"2020-01-25T06:34:40.212Z"},{"id":"893a20ec-7b70-4f17-a923-c43bfeaba0a5","url":"https://i.imgur.com/nWCIVKZ.jpg","normalizedUrl":"https://imgur.com/nWCIVKZ","thumbnail":"https://i.imgur.com/nWCIVKZl.jpg","type":"image/imgur","tags":["ANNOTATED"],"createdAt":"2020-01-25T06:34:40.212Z","updatedAt":"2020-01-25T06:34:40.212Z"}],"postAvatar":""}